                <note rend="inline" type="source">819.51/284: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Panama</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Price</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1921-01-27T18:00:00-05:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">January 27, 1921—6 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>4. Your 4, January 18, 4 p.m.</p>
                <p>Department regrets inability of President and Fiscal Agent to agree on salary,
                    and will submit name of competent successor if <pb facs="0697" n="601"
                        xml:id="pg_601"/> Ruan’s intention to leave Panama is in your opinion,
                    irrevocable. Refer to Department’s 51, December 7.<note n="2" xml:id="d526fn2"
                        >Not printed.</note>
                </p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Colby</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
